Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:55.93,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}認めてた　臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:01.93,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}わからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:12.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}怖がってた　後ろの自分が現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:17.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}幾つもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:25.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}ここはきっと儚い心を満たして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:33.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}夢で高く飛んだ身体はどんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:35.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:42.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}眠る小さな思い　広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}気づく　弱い　私　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:51.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}暗い世界　強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:57.41,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}長い夢見る心はそう永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:01.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}I wanna always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:05.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}I'll give you everything I have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:55.93,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}懦弱的过去已被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:01.93,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}但内心依旧懵懂无知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:12.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}曾经畏惧那身后的自己  如今映照出现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:17.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}几度描绘天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:25.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}这里定能填满脆弱的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:33.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}此身只为梦想而高飞  无论身缠多少不安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:35.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}都能挥之而去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:42.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}沉眠的小小心愿   不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}意识到  软弱的  我  只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:51.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}就算身处昏暗的世界  也能坚强活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:57.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}悠久梦境中的心化作了永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}遠くに聞こえた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:29.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:34.02,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}もう一度強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:41.28,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}今度は高く駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:47.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}ただ繰り返す現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.95,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:58.54,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}目指すべき明日を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:03.86,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}この思いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:10.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}目の前に開かれた果てない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:14.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}たとえ夢でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}迷い続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:22.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}夢の奥で強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:27.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}ずっと　ずっと　響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:34.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an7}そっと　そっと　光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}远方传来了钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:29.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}那钟声稍稍有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:34.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}再一次振作内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:41.28,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}这次从高空飞翔而过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:47.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}无论是不断轮回的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}还是繁星般数不胜数的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:58.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}都找到了应当前进的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:03.86,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}这份思念是战无不胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:10.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}眼前开启的是那无边无际的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:14.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}就算这只是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}就算感到迷茫与彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:22.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}也能在梦境深处坚强地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:27.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}一直  一直  不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:34.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\an1}静静  静静  闪闪发亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,395)}这个游戏从开始至今  已经过了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(350,345)\fs19}2022年12月2日  第1层 托尔巴纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,395)}在这段时间里有2000人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够突破第1层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连我这个封测玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不曾到达过BOSS的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于召开了第1层BOSS的攻略会议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\fsp-10}　{\fsp1}Beater{\r}\N封弊者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常感谢大家能响应我的召集来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蒂尔贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人认为是骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有职业系统的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说自己是骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议不会也是开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座塔的顶层发现了BOSS的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须打倒BOSS  登上第2层
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉那些在起始之城镇等待着的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个死亡游戏  总有一天能够通关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们这些现在聚集在这里的人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么虽然有些仓促
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我想召开攻略会议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先请先组一个6人的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}组队的话  我们当然要在一队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼层BOSS不是简单的队伍能够应对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那么就由我来担任队长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聚集数支队伍  组成团队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是找不到队伍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是周围的玩家看起来都是亲友队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想打扰他们罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独行玩家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}solo player，指单独行动，不与其他人组队合作的玩家，这里用了角川的名词翻译。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要不要和我组队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也听到了  BOSS靠一个人是无法攻略的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一次临时组队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,250)\fs14\be1}是否接受组队申请？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  差不多也该组好队了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫牙王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与BOSS战斗之前  有些话我想要说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有些家伙  该对那死去的2000人道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的「有些家伙」应该就是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些原封测玩家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是明摆着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些玩过封测的家伙们  在这个垃圾游戏开始的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就抛弃了新玩家一下子消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将高效的练级地点和报酬丰厚的任务都据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己练得很强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强之后还是对其他人坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之中一定有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩过封测的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不向大家下跪谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且将所有的金钱和道具交出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会也不能把性命交给这样的队友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以发言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫艾基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于原封测玩家没有照顾新玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致了新玩家的大量死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你要求他们谢罪并且赔偿  是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本攻略  你应该也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道具店有免费派发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拿到了  那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行派发的  正是原封测玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  情报我们每个人都有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有大量玩家死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要吸取这些失败的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑如何去挑战BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这才是今天我们在这里要讨论的议题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  现在可以继续开会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS的情报  其实已经记载在刚开始派发的最新版攻略上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\fsp260}　{\fsp1}Illfang the Kobold Lord{\r}\N根据这些情报  BOSS的名字是地精之王伊鲁方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\fsp180}　{\fsp1}Ruin Kobold Sentinel{\r}\N另外旁边还带有数只废墟地精守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS的武器是战斧和圆盾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HP槽有四段  进入最后一段的红血状态时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器会换为东洋系的弯刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击模式也会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻略会议到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  关于道具分配
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金钱设定为所有人平均分配
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验值由打倒怪物的队伍获得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具则由系统自动分配的人获得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}注：SAO中的道具分配方式是队伍中的任意一人随机获得，而其他人是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  明天早上10点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  解散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好吃的吧  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以坐你旁边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的觉得这个好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这个城镇以后我每天都要吃一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是吃的时候会做些加工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加工？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试把这个涂在面包上吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在前一个村庄里「逆袭的母牛」任务的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的话我告诉你窍门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这个城镇  并不是为了要吃好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了活出自我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其一直躲在最初的城镇里的旅馆  慢慢地腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如以自己的意志活到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被怪物打倒而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想输给这个游戏  这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想看到自己的队友死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少明天可别死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(350,345)\fs19}2022年12月3日  第1层 森林区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我们落单者的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\fsp190}　{\fsp1}Ruin Kobold Sentinel{\r}\N对付BOSS周围的小怪  废墟地精守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用剑技挡开它们斧枪的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就趁机进行「交换」冲上去攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是第一次组队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要说的话只有一句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A队和C队进行「交换」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B队  格挡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C队防御并准备「交换」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边后退一边准备从侧面攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D E F队 不要让守卫接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为是初学者  没想到是个不得了的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太快以至于看不清出剑的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Job
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和情报所说一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下  让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时应该采取的战术是所有队员进行包围才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是弯刀  而是野太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与封测时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力向后跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂尔贝鲁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂尔贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是封测玩家  应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到进行最后一击所奖励的稀有道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是封测玩家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把BOSS…把BOSS打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个死亡游戏刚开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只考虑着自己能够活到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了  克莱因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  蒂尔贝鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然是封测玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有扔下其他的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领着大家  出色地完成战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了我所没有做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗方式和守卫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一击要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回复完毕之前由我们来撑着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚丝娜  最后的攻击一起上  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,170)\fs16\be1\frz10}暗夜外套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的剑技  恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场胜利是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对蒂尔贝鲁先生见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗  你明明对BOSS的技能了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一开始就把那些情报说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂尔贝鲁就不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定是原封测玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以BOSS的攻击模式他全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道并且隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定还有别的封测玩家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原封测玩家？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被人和那些外行相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选中成为SAO封测玩家的1000人里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝大多数都是连怎么升级都不知道的初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你们相对来说还要厉害一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和那些家伙不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在封测时期  登上了其他所有人都没有到达过的楼层
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道BOSS的刀技能  也是因为在上方的楼层中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与用刀的怪物战斗了多次的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道很多其他事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多到连情报屋都难以企及的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的  已经不能算是封测玩家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是作弊了  作弊者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,357)\fs16}Betaer            Cheater                       Beater
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封测者和作弊者所以是封弊者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封弊者  这个称呼很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  我是封弊者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始  不要把我和原封测玩家相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在战斗中叫了我的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  直接就喊你名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说我的念法错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  除了自己以外可以看到追加的HP槽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那下面写了什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  原来一直都写在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会变强的
